MU ltirate
DI gital
S  ignal
P  rocessor

In order to install MuDiSP3 on your LINUX distribution you must follow
these steps:

1-
Be shure to have already installed the following packages on your
system:
	gcc version 3.2 (or later)
	gnuplot 3.7 (or later)
wou may need also the following packages for Linear Algebra 
Matrix comptation
	lapack-3.0
	blas-3.0
	
2-
the MuDiSP3 libraries are installed in the "/usr/local/mudisp3"
directory. If you need to change this path edit the main level
"Makefile" and modify the "MDSP3_SRC" variable

3-
execute the command "make" from within the MuDiSP3 distribution
directory

4-
if the compilation process is successful, become root and execute the
command "make install" 

5-
test the installation following the QUICKSTART note in the
/usr/local/mudisp3/doc directory.

6-
have fun !


